platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Cest le moment de se mouiller

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: This breakneck chapter in the Riptide GP series is so intense, its got us reaching for a life jacket. Or maybe several: Renegades solo campaign packs tons of water-racing events and sick tricks to master. (Split-screen local and eight-player online matches are our favorites.) However you play, stunning tracks like a gorgeous forest river deliver awesome arcade thrills. On Apple TV, it's our 2016 Game of the Year.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Manage your speed and watch out for waves in this brilliant water-racing sequel.
